MultiChoice has announced that DStv Compact Plus and Compact customers can now get Showmax for R49 per month. Showmax includes over 30,000 TV show episodes and movies, and is normally priced at R99 per month. Compact Plus and Compact subscribers will be able to access Showmax via their Explora decoder or DStv Now app, in addition to web browsers. A single Showmax subscription gives customers access to two concurrent streams on different devices, and users can download up to 25 shows and movies to their device to watch offline. A link to Showmax has been added to the DStv now app, and DStv subscribers can use up to four devices to access DStv Now simultaneously.